**Title**: IR Scanner with Secure, Real-Time Telemedicine Integration and Automated Reporting for Remote Diagnostics

**Key Idea**: Live-streaming IR scan data with automated, standardized reporting to remote clinicians enables expert consultation and documentation in underserved areas.

**Paragraph**: Portable IR scanners with secure telemedicine integration bridge frontline workers and remote specialists. Adding automated report generation (e.g., standardized summaries) supports immediate care decisions, longitudinal tracking, and quality assurance, improving outcomes in rural and underserved settings.

**Approach**: Integrate secure video/data streaming and automated reporting into IR devices; pilot in rural clinics; measure impact on clinical decision-making, reporting accuracy, and patient outcomes.

**Key References**: [Sun 2020]; [Ashok 2017].

